entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You found the three droids hiding in the depths of the Darklighter Cache. You attached the pain bolts and finished them off as requested by EV-9D9.
entries.journal_entry_description: EV-9D9 has had three droids escape her care. She believes they are taking refuge in a storage facility run by the Darklighters. EV-9D9 wants you to place a specially designed pain bolt on the droids and then destroy them. There are three targets; R3-B57, BD-34, and  RA-316.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: EV-9D9's information is that the escaped droids are hiding in the Darklighter Cache before making their way off planet. Go there and finish them off.
entries.task02_comm_message_text: You must give pain bolts in back pack to droids before you attempt to terminate them. Match pain bolt to proper droid.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: EV-9D9 has given you a pain bolt to attach to RA-316. You have to attach it first before you destroy the droid or EV-9D9 will not get the necessary transmission.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: You have applied the pain bolt to the RA unit. Its pain threshold regulators are off-line. Destroy it and the automatic recording device will send its death agonies back to EV-9D9.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: EV-9D9 has given you a pain bolt to attach to BD-34. You have to attach it first before you destroy the droid or EV-9D9 will not get the necessary transmission.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: You have applied the pain bolt to the BD unit. Its pain threshold regulators are off-line. Destroy it and the automatic recording device will send its death agonies back to EV-9D9.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: EV-9D9 has given you a pain bolt to attach to R3-B57. You have to attach it first before you destroy the droid or EV-9D9 will not get the necessary transmission.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: You have applied the pain bolt to the R3 unit. Its pain threshold regulators are off-line. Destroy it and the automatic recording device will send its death agonies back to EV-9D9.
entries.task10_comm_message_text: Very good. The synaptic responses spike well beyond the cut off levels. Return for final discussions.
entries.task11_journal_entry_description: You have destroyed the droids for EV-9D9.  Time to return to Jabba's Palace and find that head.
entries.task13_journal_entry_description: This is the location of the Darklighter Cache.
